{
  "stem": "9665.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were stationed in the-- in a place around the Hague, which was the, which was the [INAUDIBLE]-- which was-- not [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Yes, it was where they usually put up the meat and all sort of things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in charge of the food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We handed out the food as much as possible to everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there arrived-- I wanted to get-- to liquidate these garages in Zeeland .",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the, and the bridge-- I'm starting to speak Dutch-- the bridge over the [INAUDIBLE] dike didn't exist anymore, you know, which was bombed or destroyed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I organized three trucks to go to Goes and come back to the Hague.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because in the Hague, I found with the liberation there was this-- the president of, of the synagogue-- not the synagogue, from the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It will come to me in a minute-- and a few others, which they call it the center of arriving Jews from other countries or concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Dutch, I can say that to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Should I say it in Dutch?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think I should say that in Dutch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- [SPEAKING DUTCH]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew at the time, it was not a matter of having money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was the old Dutch guilder, which wasn't worth a-- wasn't worth-- not worth anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So with Melitta being with the-- in the Dutch government, I had millions of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that is what I gave them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, these are the cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never sold one cigarette ever in my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I gave it to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
